title: BelowDeckMed: Failing to Meet Eggs-pectations
description: As the Below Deck Med season limps to the finish line, Matthew gets on our every last nerve with his incessant emotional neediness. Meanwhile, Katie's boneheaded decision to end the season with two stews comes back to haunt her as Jemele Hill, Michael Eaves, and several other guests make an endless stream of requests.
author: watchwhatcrappens@gmail.com (benron)
